&lt;p&gt;Applicants are invited to apply for Locum Consultant Ophthalmologist post based at the Hillingdon Hospital and Mount Vernon Hospital sites. It will predominantly cover the Paediatric Ophthalmology Service including ROP Screening. including and complement the provision of Ophthalmology services. They will also be expected to support Hillingdon patients treated at the Western Eye Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a Locum Post to cover Maternity Leave 12 months fixed term.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameMs Sheena GeorgeJob titleClinical LeadEmail addressSheena.George@nhs.netTelephone number01895 279699Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Informal discussions regarding this post would be welcomed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Ms Sheena George/Pardip Grewal in the first instance on 01895 279699 or 01895 279732, Sheena.George@nhs.net, Pardip.Grewal@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
